             was indicted for <rs id="t18020113-62-off327" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020113-62-off327" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020113-62-off327" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18020113-62-cd328" type="crimeDate">21st of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020113-62-off327 t18020113-62-cd328"></join>, one sack, value 3s. and a bushel of wheat, value 10s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18020113-62-victim639" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Shore
                  <interp inst="t18020113-62-victim639" type="surname" value="Shore"></interp>
